@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nxjrqr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.31 * v2 + 0.48) - wp.exp(v2 + 0.58)))
    v2 = 0.32
    v0 = (v0 + (wp.exp(tmp + 0.33) * 0.46))
    tmp = wp.exp(wp.sin((v2 + 0.42 - v0 + 0.22)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.92 + v0 + 0.82)) + (tmp + v0))
    v0 = (0.64 / (wp.exp(v2 + 0.12) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.92)))
    data[tid] = v0
